data.text:
A program made for easy managing Ultrastar Deluxe files, file manager, manage and download songs, mp3s, covers, backgrounds, videos ***While development stopped in 2009, it still works on Vista and Win7***

Features

Downloads MP3's, Lyrics, Covers, Background and video in 1 click

Manages your library

Create new karaoke songs quickly from your music-library

Synchronizing video, music and lyrics is only 1 click away...
